  "operation_name": "aclnnAddRmsNormDynamicQuant",
  "description": "接口功能：RmsNorm算子是大模型常用的归一化操作，相比LayerNorm算子，其去掉了减去均值的部分。DynamicQuant算子则是为输入张量进行对称动态量化的算子。AddRmsNormDynamicQuant算子将RmsNorm前的Add算子和RmsNorm归一化输出给到的1个或2个DynamicQuant算子融合起来，减少搬入搬出操作。\n计算公式：\n\nx=x_{1}+x_{2}\n\ny = \\operatorname{RmsNorm}(x)=\\frac{x}{\\operatorname{Rms}(\\mathbf{x})}\\cdot gamma, \\quad \\text { where } \\operatorname{Rms}(\\mathbf{x})=\\sqrt{\\frac{1}{n} \\sum_{i=1}^n x_i^2+epsilon}\n\n若smoothScale1Optional和smoothScale2Optional均不输入，则y2Out和scale2Out输出无实际意义。计算过程如下所示：\n\nscale1Out=row_max(abs(y))/127\n\ny1Out=round(y/scale1Out)\n\n若仅输入smoothScale1Optional，则y2Out和scale2Out输出无实际意义。计算过程如下所示：\n\ninput = y\\cdot smoothScale1Optional\n\nscale1Out=row_max(abs(input))/127\n\ny1Out=round(input/scale1Out)\n\n若smoothScale1Optional和smoothScale2Optional均输入，则算子的五个输出均为有效输出。计算过程如下所示：\n\ninput1 = y\\cdot smoothScale1Optional\n\ninput2 = y\\cdot smoothScale2Optional\n\nscale1Out=row_max(abs(input1))/127\n\nscale2Out=row_max(abs(input2))/127\n\ny1Out=round(input1/scale1Out)\n\ny2Out=round(input2/scale2Out)\n\n其中row_max代表每行求最大值。",
  "api_flow": "two-step",
  "inter_parameter_constraints": [
    {
      "type": "shape_equality",
      "params": [
        "x1",
        "x2"
      ],
      "expr": "x1.shape == x2.shape",
      "description": "x2的shape必须与x1一致。",
      "source": "x1",
      "target": [
        "x2"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "x1",
        "x2"
      ],
      "expr": "x1.dtype == x2.dtype",
      "description": "x2的数据类型必须与x1一致。",
      "source": "x1",
      "target": [
        "x2"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "x1",
        "gamma"
      ],
      "expr": "x1.dtype == gamma.dtype",
      "description": "gamma的数据类型必须与x1一致。",
      "source": "x1",
      "target": [
        "gamma"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_dependency",
      "params": [
        "x1",
        "gamma"
      ],
      "expr": "len(gamma.shape) == 1 and gamma.shape[0] == x1.shape[-1]",
      "description": "gamma必须是一维张量，且其长度必须等于x1的最后一维。",
      "source": "x1",
      "target": [
        "gamma"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_equality",
      "params": [
        "gamma",
        "smoothScale1Optional"
      ],
      "expr": "(smoothScale1Optional is None) or (smoothScale1Optional.shape == gamma.shape)",
      "description": "smoothScale1Optional在传入时，其shape必须与gamma一致。",
      "source": "gamma",
      "target": [
        "smoothScale1Optional"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "gamma",
        "smoothScale1Optional"
      ],
      "expr": "(smoothScale1Optional is None) or (smoothScale1Optional.dtype == gamma.dtype)",
      "description": "smoothScale1Optional在传入时，其数据类型必须与gamma一致。",
      "source": "gamma",
      "target": [
        "smoothScale1Optional"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_equality",
      "params": [
        "gamma",
        "smoothScale2Optional"
      ],
      "expr": "(smoothScale2Optional is None) or (smoothScale2Optional.shape == gamma.shape)",
      "description": "smoothScale2Optional在传入时，其shape必须与gamma一致。",
      "source": "gamma",
      "target": [
        "smoothScale2Optional"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "gamma",
        "smoothScale2Optional"
